mental health insurance coverage has been working. By Robert Pear.
</P>
<P>
   NJ-BUSCRASH-VICTIMS _ The stories of the victims in the New
Jersey bus crash _ elderly people from Brooklyn, some of them
russian immigrants, going to Atlantic City in search of a bit of
glitter and excitement for their lonely lives.
</P>
<P>
   With photo.
</P>
<P>
   WINTER-STORM (Washington) _ The first winter storm of the season
in the east created a rare white Christmas in some regions of
southeastern Virginia. But it also left hundreds of thousands of
people without electricity to celebrate. By Michael Janofsky.
</P>
<P>
   FLA-BURN (Orlando, Fla.) _ Faced with more long-range drought
conditions in Florida, state officials are seeking $35 million for
an aggressive controlled-burning program to prevent a repetition of
last summer's fires, which destroyed more than 500,000 acres.
</P>
<P>
   LA-CHRISTMAS-DINNER (Los Angeles) _ On the Sunset Strip, the
garish center of Hollywood night life, strivers, dreamers and
castaways line up under the California sun for a show business
version of a homespun tradition, Christmas dinner at a comedy club.
</P>
<P>
   With photo.
