   FBN-JETS (Undated) _ He is the only linebacker still playing
from that 1986 Giants Super Bowl team. He is the only current Jet
who was with Bill Parcells on both of his championship outfits.
That, says the 34-year-old Pepper Johnson, means something this
week as he gets ready for one more installment in the stretch run
that has gone so well and will continue into January. By Gerald
Eskenazi.
