<P>
   FBN-FALCONS-DOLPHINS _ It has been the feel-good story of the
year. The Atlanta Falcons, built by Georgian Dan Reeves and
consisting of some of the most lovable, hard-working and diverse
NFL players you'll find on any team, have captured the imagination
of the city. This team has willed its way from nothing to become
the NFC West champs and national darlings, and when they face the
Dolphins today, a full house in the Georgia Dome will roar its
approval. Shades of 1991 with the Braves? You bet. (Winkeljohn,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution) 30.
</P>
