legacy and pondering ways to memorialize the man in the silver
Stetson. But now, Scottsdale, embroiled in twin scandals and public
squabbling, is getting the kind of headlines Drinkwater would have
hated. By ALEXA HAUSSLER and CAROL SOWERS. Story will move in the
``A'' category. &QL;
